Europe on a Budget
By Yehudah Leibig
State of Israel Tourist Guide

Two Sea Gate teens claim to have started out with $500 each and managed to travel Europe for 2 months. The boys hitchhiked, wandered and adventured through Europe while their stupid classmates languored over french fries at Nathan's. The two returned with long hair, strains and 2 weed eyed 'Trump II' 500 Mastergastos, they even had change left over. One of the two actually lost 40 pounds, because of the arduous foreign shortage in Europe.

[Second column continues with more text about 'Upon release, the elder brother commented, screw it, next time we'll take it to the grease firendly']

Hunchback Dies
By Nat or Lucky Luckfeld
Preschool Chronicle

Robert Avner, Coney Island's only living hunchback died last week of an infected bunch. Observers witnessed Avner screaming at his friends for help with his banana back. 'Scratch like a bitch, scratch like a bitch' he pleaded, but it was too late. An ooze-like growth had formed on the hunch. Avner died of whiplash from repeatedly turning his head to far left and far right during his last minutes.

Dirt Brothers Arrested
By Richard Freed
Tattooing Arts On Magazine

Once again, the infamous 'Dirt Brothers' were seen on Sea Gate Avenue illegally spraying drain oil from their 'Lemon' Camaro. Sol 'Gino' 'Gime' Yentsin warned the Dirt brothers Judge Phil Ruskiek issued the Dirt Brothers guilty and sentenced them to 10 life confinements with buddy Wolfie. Larry-Dick 'Dirty' Strietman, Donnie [Redacted with black bar] British [text continues but cut off]

Teen Bitten
By Mrs. Shapdowitz
Woodwork Newsletter

A Sea Gate teenager (name withheld) was viciously bitten on the neck by crazed Steve Jankowski. The bitten youth was found crying after wounds 'Count Hump' expressed the found a vat' declared [text continues]
